nail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtCdfT2o.jpg&h=4a66f66c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/3aW2xvH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3aW2xvH.jpg&h=334cc5ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿蛆曾於入行45週年大玩黑絲誘惑<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/wyKzg6i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwyKzg6i.jpg&h=dd2f2b8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/nTgqBoj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FnTgqBoj.jpg&h=2689ea4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/kOg106b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkOg106b.jpg&h=d8043d8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/qiSPdI8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqiSPdI8.jpg&h=a26ccee9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/GmLUBEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGmLUBEY.jpg&h=862c5514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&sect;更誘惑到洋腸髮型師親吻阿姐嫩滑面龐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Y4Tw6bE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FY4Tw6bE.jpg&h=43d84299&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/VjYL6Ox.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVjYL6Ox.jpg&h=1eb22340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/rNPxrEK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrNPxrEK.jpg&h=b59a8e35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/SBRnG7v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSBRnG7v.jpg&h=9b74daf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/SFeRKUZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSFeRKUZ.jpg&h=df7c8887&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/h6sv3Cg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fh6sv3Cg.jpg&h=708a8728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ujnargB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FujnargB.jpg&h=387babcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/dJcobUx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdJcobUx.jpg&h=8f0531c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&sect; 阿姐不時向觀眾展示長在其右邊白滑腋下肌膚的小痣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/FbNodf5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFbNodf5.jpg&h=64d69455&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/VVckxRX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVVckxRX.jpg&h=f642c3c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/bEN45yh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FbEN45yh.jpg&h=ce00f29a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&sect; 明言要&quot;push up&quot;自己既阿蛆夾出四吋洪溝，實在令人目不暇給，眼睛都唔知要望邊好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/1YF5Tsf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1YF5Tsf.jpg&h=c2d45d21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&sect; 阿蛆不時拋出可愛雞蘿柚既姿態，教人垂涎三尺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/rr21OS6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Frr21OS6.jpg&h=34b7b92e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&sect; 阿蛆不忘展示大腿柔軟度"},{"pid":"d41c96513158a87e9cdf06e16e6aa0e4fc811015","tid":908983,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:23:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">貴為人大既阿蛆仍熱心效忠中共，維護香港穩定發展，幫手度掂基本法<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vX4K419.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvX4K419.jpg&h=fbb5de32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲好關心香港政治添<br />\n為咗選出欣賞粵劇嘅特首,<br />\n不惜向林鄭投懷送抱<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3ohzdXSLfLZvZDFpV6/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3ohzdXSLfLZvZDFpV6%2Fgiphy.gif&h=2cb5d57d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪阿姐怒插港獨壞分子 <br />\n苦心勸他們離開香港 <br />\n勿阻香港繁榮穩定發展<br />\n「唔係中國人, 就滾出中國!!!」<br />\n「你係中國人 呢度係中國土地 如果你唔想做中國人&nbsp;咪移民去第二度囉！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9GtkBCH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9GtkBCH.jpg&h=8ce8597f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/28192338/image1472383315843.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2F28192338%2Fimage1472383315843.jpg&h=61a42ac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/Wz8k48n17XY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWz8k48n17XY&d=6bPelPYNlKPQ9BKRbB%2BhvZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=77dee51e\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/Wz8k48n17XY</a><br />\n<br />\n熱愛日本藝妓<del>女</del>文化既汪阿姐斥「支那」乃日本辱華字眼</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/xYOVb8oz_rU/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FxYOVb8oz_rU%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=475c9846&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uf87pH6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fuf87pH6.png&h=e4955f25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/I_b31aIXbvY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FI_b31aIXbvY&d=6bPelPYNlKPQ9BKRbB%2BhvZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=51e6ecaf\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/I_b31aIXbvY</a><br />\n<br />\n<span styl