 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jK351cj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjK351cj.jpg&h=07d77f8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一生為中共效力, 為人民福祉為依歸嘅阿姐背負住好沉重嘅代價</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/orVoH24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2ForVoH24.jpg&h=06a1720d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JXqBEkB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJXqBEkB.jpg&h=a6d65d46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZaUriTB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZaUriTB.jpg&h=d73cc12b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/34RAKQ6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F34RAKQ6.jpg&h=040457d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呀姐咁索都冇畀人劫色, 真係好彩</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲要搞到連fb 都冇得用, 可怒也</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160901/photo/bkn-20160901165952559-0901_00862_001_01p.jpg?20160901172223\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20160901%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20160901165952559-0901_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20160901172223&h=ffb6871d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"356731b526cd3e8ff8974eaf0d72653269f6b282","tid":908983,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:24:22.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.makeagif.com/media/5-02-2015/3wzZbC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F5-02-2015%2F3wzZbC.gif&h=af4b7fa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://vignette4.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/1/10/101.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20101016103517\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette4.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F1%2F10%2F101.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20101016103517&h=47486d8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嘔</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww3.sinaimg.cn/large/6776b853gw1esqsv3bvp0j21kw16otj6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww3.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F6776b853gw1esqsv3bvp0j21kw16otj6.jpg&h=46cd609b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鎂光燈中發亮, 不可觸摸一位<del>嘔</del>偶像</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.makeagif.com/media/5-02-2015/1vzTno.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F5-02-2015%2F1vzTno.gif&h=02963238&s={SIZE}\" />&amp;#160;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用兩手遮掩雙眼, 專心嘔吐</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/kgTrfdz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkgTrfdz.gif&h=33460a26&s={SIZE}\" />@<br />\n@by 開運招福貓 巴打<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/q67SqZN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fq67SqZN.gif&h=6907309c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/p4FSWViG-q8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fp4FSWViG-q8&d=6bPelPYNlKPQ9BKRbB%2BhvZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=d7ef5538\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/p4FSWViG-q8</a>"},{"pid":"3bd6a82efd3ffc90faa56814fb78dd7b77cdb4d6","tid":908983,"uid":222445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"218b918dab0d47db51b660df3ffc70d05e254c24","tid":908983,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:11:09.000Z","msg":"咁都可以入民進黨數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181120/1469568/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181120%2F1469568%2F&d=6bPelPYNlKPQ9BKRbB%2BhvZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=3bd75619\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181120%2F1469568%2F&h=7dfce54b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181120/1469568/</a><br />\n<br />\n「唐僧」羅家英嘆金馬獎污點　譙民進黨耍奧步<br />\n17451出版時間：2018/11/20 08:37<br />\n<br />\n港星「唐僧」羅家英日前來台擔任金馬獎頒獎嘉賓，昨表示因頒完獎就離開了，不知之後發生的爭議，「今天才知道。可惜，好好的一個電影沙龍，污點」。他接著po出與直言「中國台灣金馬獎」的涂們合照，批評民進黨手段卑鄙。<br />\n <br />\n羅家英的明星老婆汪明荃曾任中國全國政協委員，他也關心台灣選戰，在微博說：「我16號到了台北，看電視，說高雄市的韓國渝（瑜）有可能撃到（倒）民進黨搶回高雄，但評論員說大家不要小看民進黨，很會用手段，無不用其極，例如，阿扁的鎗（槍）擊等，什麼手段都用上，在重要關頭便使用，讓人防不勝防，我看後才覺得可笑，一而再再而三，仍然有人相信嗎？真的要看看有什麼厲害招數，嘩，昨晚使出了、卑鄙。」<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n以太陽花學運為主的《我們的青春，在台灣》獲最佳紀錄片，導演傅榆領獎時最後說：「我希望有一天，我們的國家可以被當作一個真正獨立的個體來看待，這是我身為一個台灣人最大的願望。」她事後解釋，「我在頒獎典禮上的發言，並不是『一時激動』，更不像部分中國網友所說的『受到民進黨政府的指使』。這是我自己一直以來就很想為這部作品所說的話」。（娛樂中心／綜合報導）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:24:31.000Z","msg":"滾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8eb898fb086f8e28927875d74843cc0add4004","tid":908983,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/30cc25.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F30cc25.gif&h=6796c7e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/30cc25.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F30cc25.gif&h=6796c7e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/30cc25.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F30cc25.gif&h=6796c7e5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}